CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 5, 1959, pg. 7, reads: "Annual Affair Thoroughly Enjoyed by Youngsters - Courier Newsboys Play, Eat, Win Prizes at Picnic -Hail, Hail! The Gang's All Here"
TitMainTitle: Crowd of boys gathered around boy in center wearing patterned short sleeve shirt, seated on grill of fire pit in South Park during Pittsburgh Courier Newsboy Picnic
